    "zh": "垂荡弹簧、减振器与惯容器",
    "en": "Heave spring, damper and inerter"
  },
  "summary": {
    "zh": "F1 悬架把车身的「点头」式整体起伏（垂荡）与单侧颠簸分开处理：专用的垂荡弹簧与减振器控制气动工作高度，惯容器则用飞轮把加速度变成可调阻尼。",
    "en": "F1 suspension separates the body's pitch/heave from single-wheel bumps: a dedicated heave spring and damper control the aerodynamic ride height, while the inerter turns acceleration into tunable damping via a flywheel."
  },
  "sourceIds": ["source-book-f1-illustrated-engineering"],
